58":"1558年","1501":"1501年","1479":"1479年","1500":"1500年","1478":"1478年","1488":"1488年","1521":"1521年","1596":"1596年","1485":"1485年","1527":"1527年","1449":"1449年","Henley-on-Thames, Oxfordshire, England":"英國奧可福爾亨利--坦斯","St Helen Bishopsgate, London, England, United Kingdom":"英國英格蘭倫敦聖 海倫 比曉普斯蓋特","Oxfordshire, England":"英國奧可福爾","North Mymms, Hertfordshire, England":"英國賀特福爾諾斯 米姆斯","lifeSummary":"Sir Robert Knollys是Robert Knollys和Elizabeth Troutbeck的兒子，於1481年出生在英國賀特福爾諾斯 米姆斯。他和Lettice Peniston至少有1個兒子。他於1509年被列為he continued in the same office under henry viii, and received an annuity of £20, on 15 november 1509, and a grant of upclatford, called rookes manor, in hampshire — part of the confiscated property of sir richard empson — on 10 february 1510/11. 。他去世於1521年在英國奧可福爾亨利--坦斯享年40歲，埋葬在英國英格蘭倫敦聖 海倫 比曉普斯蓋特。"},"zh-hans":{"1481–1521":"1481年–1521年","1478–1527":"1478年–1527年","1479–1501":"1479年–1501年","1485–1558":"1485年–1558年","1514–1596":"1514年–1596年","1449–Male":"1449年–殁","–Female":"殁","9 July 1514":"1514年7月9日","15 November 1509":"1509年11月15日","1481":"1481年","13 November 1520":"1520年11月13日","1514":"1514年","1558":"1558年","1501":"1501年","1479":"1479年","1500":"1500年","1478":"1478年","1488":"1488年","1521":"1521年","1596":"1596年","1485":"1485年","1527":"1527年","1449":"1449年","Henley-on-Thames, Oxfordshire, England":"英国奧可福爾亨利--坦斯","St Helen Bishopsgate, London, England, United Kingdom":"英国英格兰倫敦聖 海倫 比曉普斯蓋特","Oxfordshire, England":"英国奧可福爾","North Mymms, Hertfordshire, England":"英国賀特福爾諾斯 米姆斯","lifeSummary":"Sir Robert Knollys是Robert Knollys和Elizabeth Troutbeck的儿子，于1481年出生在英国賀特福爾諾斯 米姆斯。他和Lettice Peniston至少有1个儿子。他于1509年被列为he continued in the same office under henry viii, and received an annuity of £20, on 15 november 1509, and a grant of upclatford, called rookes manor, in hampshire — part of the confiscated property of sir richard empson — on 10 february 1510/11. 。他去世于1521年在英国奧可福爾亨利--坦斯享年40岁，埋葬在英国英格兰倫敦聖 海倫 比曉普斯蓋特。"},"hr":{"1481–1521":"1481.–1521.","1478–1527":"1478–1527","1479–1501":"1479–15