 di 28 anni, la sua occupazione è indicata come he continued in the same office under henry viii, and received an annuity of £20, on 15 november 1509, and a grant of upclatford, called rookes manor, in hampshire — part of the confiscated property of sir richard empson — on 10 february 1510/11. . Morì nel 1521, nel Henley-on-Thames, Oxfordshire, England, all'età di 40 anni, e fu sepolto a St Helen Bishopsgate, London, Inghilterra, Regno Unito."},"ja":{"1481–1521":"1481年–1521年","1478–1527":"1478年–1527年","1479–1501":"1479年–1501年","1485–1558":"1485年–1558年","1514–1596":"1514年–1596年","1449–Male":"1449年–死亡","–Female":"死亡","9 July 1514":"1514年7月9日","15 November 1509":"1509年11月15日","1481":"1481年","13 November 1520":"1520年11月13日","1514":"1514年","1558":"1558年","1501":"1501年","1479":"1479年","1500":"1500年","1478":"1478年","1488":"1488年","1521":"1521年","1596":"1596年","1485":"1485年","1527":"1527年","1449":"1449年","Henley-on-Thames, Oxfordshire, England":"イギリスオクスフォードシュアイアヘンリー-オン-サムス","St Helen Bishopsgate, London, England, United Kingdom":"イギリスイギリスロンドンスト ヘレン ビショプスガト","Oxfordshire, England":"イギリスオクスフォードシュアイア","North Mymms, Hertfordshire, England":"イギリスハートフォードシュアイアノース ムインムズ","lifeSummary":"Sir Robert Knollysは1481年にイギリスハートフォードシュアイアノース ムインムズでRobert KnollysとElizabeth Troutbeckの息子として生まれた。彼はLettice Penistonとの間に少なくとも1人の息子をもうけた。1509年，28歳の時，職業はhe continued in the same office under henry viii, and received an annuity of £20, on 15 november 1509, and a grant of upclatford, called rookes manor, in hampshire — part of the confiscated property of sir richard empson — on 10 february 1510/11. と記録されている。彼は1521年にイギリスオクスフォードシュアイアヘンリー-オン-サムスで40歳で死去し，イギリスイギリスロンドンスト ヘレン ビショプスガトにて埋葬された。"},"ko":{"1481–1521":"1481년–1521년","1478–1527":"1478년–1527년","1479–1501":"1479년–1501년","1485–1558":"1485년–1558년","1514–1596":"1514년–1596년","1449–Male":"1449년–사망","–Female":"사망","9 July 1514":"1514년 7월 9일","15 November 1509":"1509년 11월 15일","1481":"1481년","13 November 1520":"1520년 11월 13일","1514":"1514년","1558":"1558년","1501":"